# Title: Harvesting Of Wifi Credentials Via Netsh.EXE
# Author: Andreas Hunkeler (@Karneades), oscd.community
# Date: 2020-04-20
# Level: medium
# Description: Detect the harvesting of wifi credentials using netsh.exe
# MITRE Tactic: Discovery
# Tags: attack.discovery, attack.credential-access, attack.t1040
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_netsh_wifi_credential_harvesting.yml

CommandLine="*wlan*" CommandLine="* s*" CommandLine="* p*" CommandLine="* k*" CommandLine="*=clear*" Image="*\\netsh.exe" OR OriginalFileName="netsh.exe"